# Local development secrets.
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in your own values:
#   cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars
#
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored and must NEVER be committed.
# For production, set secrets via: npx wrangler secret put JWT_SECRET

# Secret used to sign HS256 JWTs (signup/login tokens). Use a long random string.
# Generate one with, for example:
#   node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(48).toString('base64url'))"
JWT_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-secret-string
